  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feeling your computer desktop is a bit dull?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desktop Kitty is coming!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085770/extras/da73aeaeb881cda9d46b935a22bc8447.webp?t=1729219961\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085770/extras/da73aeaeb881cda9d46b935a22bc8447.poster.avif?t=1729219961\" class=\"bb_img\" width=250 height=50 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This adorable little kitten will accompany you while you work, study, or just daydream...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kitty will remind you to take breaks on time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And who knows, Kitty might even bring you special gifts~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085770/extras/ddec24a85b29a966a8cf7708734495e4.webp?t=1729219961\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085770/extras/ddec24a85b29a966a8cf7708734495e4.poster.avif?t=1729219961\" class=\"bb_img\" width=93 height=48 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cat On My Desktop is an adorable idle game featuring a cute cat pet for your desktop. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While it's idling,  kitty will bring back all sorts of gifts for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect these gifts to learn about  kitty's adventurous life and unlock achievements too~</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feeling your computer desktop is a bit dull?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desktop Kitty is coming!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085770/extras/da73aeaeb881cda9d46b935a22bc8447.webp?t=1729219961\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085770/extras/da73aeaeb881cda9d46b935a22bc8447.poster.avif?t=1729219961\" class=\"bb_img\" width=250 height=50 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This adorable little kitten will accompany you while you work, study, or just daydream...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kitty will remind you to take breaks on time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And who knows, Kitty might even bring you special gifts~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085770/extras/ddec24a85b29a966a8cf7708734495e4.webp?t=1729219961\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085770/extras/ddec24a85b29a966a8cf7708734495e4.poster.avif?t=1729219961\" class=\"bb_img\" width=93 height=48 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cat On My Desktop is an adorable idle game featuring a cute cat pet for your desktop. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While it's idling,  kitty will bring back all sorts of gifts for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect these gifts to learn about  kitty's adventurous life and unlock achievements too~</p>",
